name: Adana Drawer Liners
description:
Looking for the fussy, floral, powder scented liners of your grandmother's heyday? Yeah, we weren't either. We've upgraded our liners to be even better this season. Larger, on a 6 foot roll, and featuring gorgeous essential oil scents. Available for pre-order shipping September 7th. 

Scent Story: black currant, blood orange & amber 

Specs:
-26 in x 6 ft
-printed in the US with water based inks
-scented with essential oils
-not adhesive

Other ways to think about your fab liners:
-makes a great hostess gift
-perfect for unique holiday gifts
-gift wrap
-line the back of a bookcase in color & pattern

name: Lattice Dopp Kit
description:
I was reminiscing one day. Every morning I would run my little knobby knees to the back of our house and watch my uncles begin their morning routine. Smelly shaving cream, straight edge razor, and sink full of water. They would pull their grooming tools from a worn leather dopp kit and begin crafting meticulous mustaches. This is our homage to those magic kits, in our signature patterns and colors. 

Specs: 
-linen/cotton blend fabric 
-waterbased, no VOC inks 
-waterproof lining 
-slim Italian leather handle 
-9"w, 5"h, 4"d
-cobalt blue

............................................................ 
MADE TO ORDER 
Please allow 2-3 weeks for your product to be made 
............................................................
Care: spot clean, wipe inside with damp cloth, do not launder
